  "name": "SecuritizedDataQualityAgent",
  "description": "A single autonomous AI agent for a buy-side investment management firm that ingests unstructured securitized product documents, extracts Critical Data Elements (CDEs), maps them to the FIBO ontology, and performs automated validation against source system records. The agent surfaces discrepancies, misclassifications (e.g., AT1/CoCo bonds), dual CUSIP linkage gaps (144A/Reg S), and benchmark transition errors for human analyst review, while maintaining full BCBS 239-compliant data lineage from source document to reported risk figure.",
